title: WebLogic Server component of Oracle
extract: The following sections briefly describe some of the Oracle WebLogic Server core components:Oracle WebLogic Server Web Services.Oracle Coherence.JMS Messaging Standard.Enterprise Grid Messaging.JRockit.Tuxedo.Oracle TopLink.
